01:22:31,852 --> 01:22:32,997
I couldn't sleep.

1519
01:22:34,005 --> 01:22:35,678
This rain and those drums.

1520
01:22:37,079 --> 01:22:39,583
And then .. thinking about tomorrow.

1521
