1648
01:33:06,220 --> 01:33:07,721
I'm sorry for him.

1649
01:33:08,838 --> 01:33:10,382
And I'm sorry for you.

1650
01:33:13,183 --> 01:33:13,969
I'm sorry.

1651
01:33:14,531 --> 01:33:16,274
For everybody in the world, I guess.

